      "repair_reason": "- [P1] Human merge review remains needed because the contributor must add real behavior proof and maintainers must accept the fail-closed attribution compatibility contract.; Cleared: The diff tightens a Worker authorization boundary and adds regression tests; I found no new supply-chain, secret-handling, or security-boundary regression. (sha=70215b302aea3d5c9a735af869614a371d44915a)",
